{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb7ba2720-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s565"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"565"},"text":"§ 565.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Establishment of committee","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb7ba2721-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s565/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Establishment.—","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb7ba2722-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s565/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Determination to establish committee","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"If after considering comments and applications submitted under section 564, the agency determines that a negotiated rulemaking committee can adequately represent the interests that will be significantly affected by a proposed rule and that it is feasible and appropriate in the particular rulemaking, the agency may establish a negotiated rulemaking committee. In establishing and administering such a committee, the agency shall comply with chapter 10 of this title with respect to such committee, except as otherwise provided in this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb7ba2723-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s565/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Determination not to establish committee","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"If after considering such comments and applications, the agency decides not to establish a negotiated rulemaking committee, the agency shall promptly publish notice of such decision and the reasons therefor in the Federal Register and, as appropriate, in trade or other specialized publications, a copy of which shall be sent to any person who applied for, or nominated another person for membership on the negotiating ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002022"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002022"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original. Probably should be “negotiated”."}],"tail":" rulemaking committee to represent such interests with respect to the proposed rule."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb7ba2724-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s565/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Membership","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The agency shall limit membership on a negotiated rulemaking committee to 25 members, unless the agency head determines that a greater number of members is necessary for the functioning of the committee or to achieve balanced membership. Each committee shall include at least one person representing the agency.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb7ba2725-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s565/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Administrative Support","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The agency shall provide appropriate administrative support to the negotiated rulemaking committee, including technical assistance.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb7ba2726-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/648/s3/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–648, § 3(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-29"},"text":"Nov. 29, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/4972"},"text":"104 Stat. 4972","children":[],"tail":", § 585; renumbered § 565 and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/354/s3/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–354, § 3(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", (3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-08-26"},"text":"Aug. 26, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/944"},"text":"106 Stat. 944","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/286/s4/a/7"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–286, § 4(a)(7)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/4305"},"text":"136 Stat. 4305","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb7ba2727-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb7ba2728-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idb7ba2729-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2022—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/286"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–286","children":[],"tail":" substituted “chapter 10 of this title” for “the Federal Advisory Committee Act”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/354/s3/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–354, § 3(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s585"},"text":"section 585 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/354/s3/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–354, § 3(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “section 564” for “section 584”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
